==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: palatalized
<hw>palatalized</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <fld>(Linguistics, Phonology)</fld>
<def>Produced with the front of the tongue near or touching the hard
palate as "y"; or with the blade of the tongue near the hard palate as
"ch" in "chin" or "j" in "gin".</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> palatal.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Palate</ent>⟦br⟧
